 would promote healthier eating habits which would benefit both food stamp recipients and taxpayers:\r\n\r\n', u'\r\n\r\nOppoents, however, contend that the bill would neither promote healthier eating nor reduce fraud:\r\n\r\n', u'\r\n\r\n\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 16 May 2015\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
