t aspect of the story was speculative, and as others have ", u', the news media tend to highlight negative events rather than positive ones: "reporters don\'t report buildings that don\'t burn."\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 30 December 2012\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
