ght opt to decline some or all of his salary, or donate it to charity).  Members of Congress could vote to decrease their salaries (which are currently set at $174,000 per year), although they have already voted to ', u' their cost-of-living pay increases in 2009 and again in 2010.\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 13 January 2011\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
