to do so.\r\n", u"\r\nThe individual health insurance mandate is one of keystones of the Affordable Care Act's implementation.  If it were truly optional rather than a requirement, then that fact would long since have been thoroughly publicized to the point of being common knowledge.  It wouldn't be an obscure nugget of information hidden in the depths of the ", u' revealed only through unreliable conspiracy web sites and social media posts.\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 17 January 2014\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
