l fishing in the U.S. is set to be banned entirely is an exceedingly far-fetched one.  The task force's ", u' report of September 2009 contained nothing that could reasonably be interpreted as suggesting such a ban was in the offing. \r\n', u"\r\nESPN subsequently issued an editor's ", u' to the editorial that originally touched off the "fishing ban" brouhaha:\r\n\r\n', u'\r\n\r\n', u' \xa0 10 March 2010\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
