sinesses do so.  Some companies may continue to redeem store gift cards while they reorganize, while others may temporarily suspend redemption of gift cards for some period of time and resume it later.  That any particular retail business has recently filed for ', u'  protection does not automatically mean that any gift cards or gift certificates it has previously issued will "not be valid for much longer."\r\n', u'\r\nFinally, not all the companies listed in the warning quoted above have filed for ', u' protection yet (and may or may not eventually do so), as detailed below:\r\n\r\n', u'\r\n\r\n', u' \xa0  5 July 2010\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n\xa0\r\n', u'\r\n\r\n'] @@@
