, u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\nThis "reasonable expectation of privacy," however, does not apply to law enforcement officials in certain situations. The ', u' reports the new legislation will make it easier for police to eavesdrop without a warrant:\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 9 December 2014\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
