 and not all branches of all fast food outlets offer hand wipes, regardless of the eateries\' halal status. \r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 29 September 2014\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
