ecause he wants to be recognized as the real father, and he\'ll take it down just as soon as Bristol calls him.\r\n', u'\r\nDozens of holes could be poked in the story laid out by "Kevin" in his video confession, but for simplicity\'s sake we\'ll list just a few of the most glaring inconsistencies:\r\n\r\n', u"\r\n\r\nIn case all that isn't convincing enough, Kevin confessed to the ", u' in a subsequent video.\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 15 September 2008\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n\xa0\r\n', u'\r\n\r\n'] @@@
