hey were supposedly spoken, rather than immediately afterwards.\r\n", u'\r\nHillary Clinton did sit for an ', u" with ABC's Diane Sawyer which aired on ", u' 2014, after which she was ', u' by some commentators (as she had been before) for not being able to provide a succinct or definitive answer when questioned about her top or proudest accomplishments as Secretary of State.  But nothing like the passage quoted above was spoken by Clinton during that ABC interview.\r\n', u'\r\n', u' \xa0 2 May 2015\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n', u'\r\n'] @@@
